          From the manufacturer

          Comfort Meets Clean in Every Bag

          Soft, Safe Bedding for Happy Small Pets

          Create a cozy, healthy home with Oxbow Pure Comfort White Bedding. Ideal for rabbits, guinea pigs, hamsters, rats, and ferrets. This premium paper bedding is ultra-soft, super absorbent, and 99.9% dust-free for a clean, pet-safe environment.

          Soft, Safe, and Superior Bedding for Every Small Pet

          Oxbow Pure Comfort Bedding—available in White, Natural, and Blend—is more than just something to line your litter box; it's a high-performance, pet-safe solution crafted for the comfort and well-being of small pets. Whether you need bedding for guinea pigs, rabbits, hamsters, rats, or ferrets, this premium small animal bedding delivers exceptional absorbency, low dust, and soft textures to support healthy rest and natural behaviors. Choose the White option for a clean, bright appearance that makes it easy to monitor your pet’s waste and health. Prefer a more natural look? The Brown (Natural) bedding offers an earthy tone made from unbleached paper. Or go with the Blend variety for a mix of white and brown that offers the best of both. All three versions are made from 100% pure, never-printed paper that’s free from inks, dyes, and additives—giving you the peace of mind that comes from using only pet-safe litter. Oxbow Pure Comfort is ideal for use in all types of small animal habitats, including guinea pig habitats, ferret habitats, and bunny litter boxes. Whether you're starting fresh with bunny supplies or upgrading your rat bedding setup, Oxbow offers the flexibility and quality pet parents expect. Each bag of bedding delivers high absorbency to control odors and moisture while remaining gentle on sensitive paws. The 99.9% dust-free formula promotes better respiratory health, especially important for small animals prone to irritation. It works great in litter box trays, rabbit litter boxes, or spread across a full enclosure. You can use it alone or in combination with other materials like pellet litter or paper litter for a multi-layer system tailored to your pet’s needs. This bedding is not only absorbent but also soft enough for nesting, burrowing, and sleeping—whether you’re filling a hamster bedding area, layering bunny bedding, or adding to your ferret litter routine. Oxbow bedding performs reliably across the board. It’s also an eco-conscious choice, made from responsibly sourced materials that help reduce environmental impact while keeping your pet’s space clean and cozy. The large litter box-friendly bag size ensures long-lasting use, making it perfect for busy households or multi-pet homes. Pet parents love the versatility of Oxbow bedding, which functions equally well as rabbit bedding, guinea pig bedding, rat bedding, or even bedding for exotic species in need of low-dust solutions. With options to match your preferred look and functionality—whether that’s crisp white paper, a rich brown tone, or a balanced blend—Oxbow makes it easy to customize your pet's habitat. Use it in a bunny litter box or across the floor of a guinea pig habitat, and you’ll notice the difference in cleanliness and comfort right away. This paper bedding for small animals is also compatible with a wide range of litter boxes, including large rabbit litter boxes, compact trays, and everything in between. Whether you're shopping for hamster supplies, bunny litter, or pet bedding that minimizes cleanup, Oxbow Pure Comfort delivers on all fronts. It’s more than just bedding—it’s a foundation for healthier, happier pets. Elevate your litter and bedding routine with Oxbow Pure Comfort, and give your small animals the clean, soft environment they deserve.

The White bedding is great for easy health monitoring, the Natural option provides an organic aesthetic, and the Blend gives you a clean, balanced look.             Product Description

            Pure, soft, and white as snow—Oxbow’s Pure Comfort White Bedding is specially designed to create the ultimate cozy space for your pets. Crafted from 100% pure, never-printed white paper, this premium bedding provides a clean, safe, and ultra-soft environment for rabbits, guinea pigs, hamsters, ferrets, rats, and other small animals. Whether you're setting up a guinea pig cage, a hamster cage, or a ferret cage, this bedding ensures superior comfort and protection. Our bedding is not only perfect for cages but also ideal for use in a rabbit litter box, guinea pig litter box, or bunny litter box, delivering odor control and moisture absorption. This white bedding is a must-have addition to your bunny supplies, guinea pig bedding, and hamster supplies. Its soft, dust-free texture supports respiratory health, making it a pet-safe litter choice. Great for litter boxes of all sizes, including large litter boxes and litter box trays, Oxbow's bedding keeps your pets' habitats fresh and dry.             Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

            To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
